699
01:14:38,069 --> 01:14:39,400
Crush his face!

700
01:14:43,808 --> 01:14:45,207
- Do it!
- Take him out!

701
01:14:45,376 --> 01:14:46,968
Drop it! Drop it!

702
01:15:08,867 --> 01:15:10,198
God.

703
01:15:29,420 --> 01:15:31,115
Linen run!

704
01:15:31,289 --> 01:15:34,884
