01:28:19,130 --> 01:28:21,894
Bring him in here! Come on!

859
01:28:27,673 --> 01:28:29,641
Come on!

860
01:28:38,283 --> 01:28:40,274
Rape this.

861
01:28:42,821 --> 01:28:47,690
My face! My face is burning!
My face!

