What are you gonna do with that?

871
01:31:26,152 --> 01:31:27,813
You okay, Frank?

872
01:31:28,387 --> 01:31:30,218
I'm okay, Dallas.

873
01:31:31,090 --> 01:31:34,218
You can trust me, Frank.
You can trust me.

874
01:31:34,494 --> 01:31:37,554
- Put it down, Dallas.
- Put it down.

875
